From: Your Name <your@email.com>
Date: Sun, 24 May 2026 12:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] mtd: spinand: add full FudanMicro driver with FM25G02B ECC fix

Add complete FMSH SPI NAND driver supporting FM25G02B with correct OOB layout
and ECC status handler to prevent stability issues.

Signed-off-by: Your Name <your@email.com>
---
